Commodity Trend Strategy Research — Project Spec
Purpose
Evaluate whether trend-following strategies on commodity futures produce a viable trading strategy meeting absolute-return-with-bounded-drawdown criteria. The output is a go/no-go decision on commodity trend deployment, plus a clear understanding of which trend variants work and which don't.
This is research, not deployment. The indices strategy remains the locked baseline; commodity trend either earns its place as an addition or replacement, or it doesn't.
What we're testing
Three trend strategy variants on the same commodity basket. The variants are designed to test different hypotheses about where trend-following edge lives in commodities. Comparing them tells us which family of trend signals matters, not just whether trend works overall.
